'''Iravati''' (''irāvatī'' in [[IAST]] transliteration) is a character in the mythology of [[India]]. She is a daughter of [[Kadru]] and [[Kasyapa]]. She is the mother of [[Airavata]], the mount of [[Indra]]. She is also associated with a sacred [[Ravi River| river]].
